reviewText: Love is needed and  must be learned. Hate is taught at different levels. Love has different levels and meanings one kind doesn't fit all. Like has been confused for lust, lust been confused with like, lust has violated all boundaries what was thought to be love is only been fleshly lust, pain, confusion, embarrassment and  more confusion.
I made all 3 of my grown children and their spouses watch this..it's wonderful,helpful and FUNNY.I highly recommend. This is Christian based and delightful.
My wife and I have been married for 37 years. We have found this to be the most helpful training tool we have ever come across.
